title: Mount Loch
text: Mount Loch is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in the <a href="Victorian%20Alps">Victorian Alps</a> of the <a href="Great%20Dividing%20Range">Great Dividing Range</a>, located in the <a href="Australia">Australia</a>n state of <a href="Victoria%20%28Australia%29">Victoria</a>. The <a href="summit">summit</a> of Mount Loch is at and it is the fourth highest mountain in the state.
